The paper discusses the performance analysis and optimization of cache-aided wireless networks, which involves topics related to network infrastructure, information theory, system engineering, multimedia, and distributed computing. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
